org.sxb.http.converter.AbstractHttpMessageConverter

  • AbstractHttpMessageConverterを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.http.converter
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter abstraction to convert between Java objects and HTTP input/output messages.
    org.sxb.http.converter.json
    实现了Jackson跟FastJson Json String to Object Object to Json String Provides an HttpMessageConverter implementations for handling JSON.
    org.sxb.http.converter.xml
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter implementations for handling XML.

    • org.sxb.http.converter.jsonでのAbstractHttpMessageConverterの使用

      org.sxb.http.converter.jsonでのAbstractHttpMessageConverterのサブクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  AbstractJackson2HttpMessageConverter
      reference Spring4.1 Abstract base class for Jackson based and content type independent HttpMessageConverter implementations.
      class  FastJsonHttpMessageConverter
      Implementation of HttpMessageConverter that can read and write JSON using fastJson1.26 This converter can be used to bind to typed beans, or untyped HashMap instances.
      class  MappingJackson2HttpMessageConverter
      Implementation of HttpMessageConverter that can read and write JSON using Jackson 2.x's ObjectMapper.

    • org.sxb.http.converter.xmlでのAbstractHttpMessageConverterの使用

      org.sxb.http.converter.xmlでのAbstractHttpMessageConverterのサブクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  AbstractJaxb2HttpMessageConverter<T>
      Abstract base class for HttpMessageConverters that use JAXB2.
      class  AbstractXmlHttpMessageConverter<T>
      Abstract base class for HttpMessageConverters that convert from/to XML.
      class  MappingJackson2XmlHttpMessageConverter
      Implementation of HttpMessageConverter that can read and write XML using Jackson 2.x extension component for reading and writing XML encoded data.
